reviewText: was definitely pleased with this movie

Pretty good early 70's made-for-TV Western.  A group of female convicts are promised a pardon if they pose as settlers and help the army transport weapons.  I hope this film is released to DVD very soon.
Good goofy old T.V. movie. Hadn't seen it in forty years. Seemed a bit cut-up.
When I saw this movie the third time I now think this movie is one of the stupidest westerns I've seen.
